		<doc link="http://doc.koolphp.net/Controls/KoolSlideMenu/Javascript/SlideMenuParent_Class/index.php#collapse">Javascript :: SlideMenuParent :: collapse()</doc>
		<doc link="http://doc.koolphp.net/Controls/KoolSlideMenu/Javascript/SlideMenuChild_Class/index.php#select">Javascript :: SlideMenuChild :: select()</doc>
